教訓之後，<br />\n嚴格定價3000!，監理，審計現場跟蹤，並且免費保修1億年。<br />\n德國人嚇跑了，印度人報價 3000，中國人來了，無償修好，免費保修2億年，但要5萬年的管理權，上帝同意了，於是中國人修好了後在門口設了個收費站，投胎每人每次500，雙向收費上不封頂，多給錢的投胎到美國，給500的投到歐洲，逃費的一律投到中國。"},{"pid":"89f2da803a4a80368f720c35fe3366ef161ce3fa","tid":1335970,"uid":166245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T18:36:23.000Z","msg":"仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0c1d1b1e61e4e9aa0500c48bf7f3bd6f22cfd49","tid":1335970,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T18:36:52.000Z","msg":"真係無恥到極"},{"pid":"f9ca01478dcd2ab09d8ceded9b36b0830bb558eb","tid":1335970,"uid":143435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T18:37:39.000Z","msg":"佢自己公佈做衰左幾多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d409cd70d462fe63309c2924fcd21f79560fb4a9","tid":1335970,"uid":166245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T18:38:09.000Z","msg":"問責制？問咗去邊<br />\n呢幾年嚟問過責嘅好似得南丫島沉船事件"},{"pid":"dc8ad9cc1e8257f77a4fa056462682385c13178c","tid":1335970,"uid":180173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T18:38:25.000Z","msg":"真係好撚垃圾個政府"},{"pid":"123efa1b8c2d820df895558db113933c515d20cf","tid":1335970,"uid":26661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T18:38:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05ce8e0ef92fc7e6d039c80e31bd7d3386141dcd","tid":1335970,"uid":166245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6121f7fc9f97aaf592d4bbfb373c6035b715d60a","tid":1335970,"uid":132572,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8f696fbac219fa5567591f6eef8f8b50e5563cff","tid":1335970,"uid":58841,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T18:28:37.000Z","msg":"老實講我恨不得佢戰線越開越多<br />\n因為單單野持分者都唔同<br />\n開越多就代表越多人瀨野同醒覺"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T18:29:46.000Z","msg":"所以要比多D持分者見到<br />\n知道政府無撚得救"},"citedBy":0,"reply